Why I started Stand Up To Trash ~ 
I pick up trash for the enormous satisfaction it brings me. The ocean gives me so much positive energy every time I walk on the beach or enter the water on my board. The bounty of sea life I get to see and play with gives me so much inspiration. I feel that I‚Äôve earned the gift of seeing them after I‚Äôve cleaned up plastic and other trash from their home.¬†Also knowing the effects trash and pollution have on our life and aquatic life. 

As¬†Program Director I‚Äôm passionately committed to bringing our community together and the mission. 

Mission: 
To protect and conserve our ocean through environmental education and raising awareness of the effects from plastic pollution by cleaning the waterways for future generations.

Funds will be used for supplies, materials, permits and expenses for a safe beach and ocean clean up and campaign.¬†
Stand Up To Trash is implementing¬†clean ups at a grassroots level and with every clean up it has a positive impact on our local beaches and ocean.¬†
