I am really focused on trying to make changes in my life to help the environment yet society I feel like is pushing back. I feel like this illustration by @eviegraceillustration demonstrates what‚Äôs in my heart right now. Surely this is not the way? 

Jumping to disposable is not the way, there are beautiful reusable masks, and maybe we don‚Äôt need a takeaway coffee? You could sit in if allowed? 

And please don‚Äôt litter. Our planet still needs us to play our part ‚ù§Ô∏èüåè

